A video of a man hawking piggybanks made from iron with names of Nigerian banks written on it is trending on Tiktok. In the video, the man is seen hawking piggy banks with Kuda Bank, Zenith Bank, First Bank, UBA and other prominent bank names written on it. A group of people who spotted him with his goods and stopped him because of his branding were seen asking for the names of their banks. ALSO READ: Naira scarcity: More commercial banks shut down operations in Lagos Voices in the video can be heard saying, “Opay no dey there, Opay nko? where Kuda?, Where POS?” Many people have since reacted to the video praising the man for his brilliance in branding bank names on each piggybank. 